episode_title: The Death And Life Of Otto Bloom
title: The Death And Life Of Otto Bloom
episode_name: The Death And Life Of Otto Bloom
description: The chronicle of the life and great love of Otto Bloom, an extraordinary man who experiences time in reverse - passing backwards through the years only remembering the future. (2016)
description2: The chronicle of the life and great love of Otto Bloom, an extraordinary man who experiences time in reverse - passing backwards through the years only remembering the future.

title: Suburban Mayhem
description: When her father threatens to contact social services and take away her child, Katrina sets in motion a plan to wreak suburban mayhem that will leave a community in shock and Katrina infamous in a way she never dreamed of. (2006)
description2: When her father threatens to contact social services and take away her child, Katrina sets in motion a plan to wreak suburban mayhem that will leave a community in shock and Katrina infamous in a way she never dreamed of.

title: Buried
description: Paul Conroy is not ready to die but when he wakes up six feet underground, poor reception, a rapidly draining battery and a dwindling oxygen supply are his worst enemies in a tightly confined race against time. (2010)
description2: Paul Conroy is not ready to die but when he wakes up six feet underground, poor reception, a rapidly draining battery and a dwindling oxygen supply are his worst enemies in a tightly confined race against time.

title: All That Jazz
description: The story of a gifted choreographer whose compulsions, both professionally and personally, lead to his destruction. (1979)
description2: The story of a gifted choreographer whose compulsions, both professionally and personally, lead to his destruction.

episode_title: Last Man Standing: Suge Knight and the Murders of Biggie & Tupac
title: Last Man Standing: Suge Knight and the Murders of Biggie & Tupac
episode_name: Last Man Standing: Suge Knight and the Murders of Biggie & Tupac
description: This film takes a look at Death Row and L.A.'s street gang culture. It would be this world of gang rivalry and dirty cops that would claim the lives of the world's two greatest rappers, Tupac Shakur and Biggie Smalls. (2021)
description2: This film takes a look at Death Row and L.A.'s street gang culture. It would be this world of gang rivalry and dirty cops that would claim the lives of the world's two greatest rappers, Tupac Shakur and Biggie Smalls.

title: Pinchgut Opera: Handel in Italy
description: Erin Helyard, Taryn Fiebig and the musicians of Pinchgut Opera perform Baroque masterworks by Handel, written when the composer was in Italy during this 20s. Filmed live at the Eugene Goossens Hall, ABC Ultimo.
